main event: A bright, silvery, circular object, about 30-40 ft in diameter, hovered about 300-500 ft above the ground for approximately 15-20 minutes.
interesting points: Several witnesses observed the object, which also gave off a humming sound.
The object then ascended vertically and disappeared from sight.
The witness reported the sighting to the local police immediately.
The object appeared to be metallic and reflecting some of the moon's light.
Dark linear masses were moving rapidly toward or away from the object, indicating dynamic forces at work.
